</li>
<li>
<div>Unlimited user definable job cost                                                   types. (i.e. Labor, Material,                                                   Subs, Equip, Other, etc.)</div>
</li>
<li>
<div>Utilized job cost information                                                   entered into the system to                                                   facilitate billings.</div>
</li>
